S. Africa’s Eskom to Develop Hydroelectric Power Project, Business Says

-- B y   G o r d o n   B e l l
-- 
2011-05-06T06:19:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-06/s-africa-s-eskom-to-develop-hydroelectric-power-project-business-says.html
Eskom Holdings Ltd.,  South Africa ’s
power utility, and the Democratic Republic of Congo plan to
proceed with the Inga III hydropower project,  Business Report 
said, citing Energy Minister Dipuo Peters.  South African President  Jacob Zuma  and Congo President
Joseph Kabila have been in discussions on the project, the
Johannesburg-based newspaper’s website cited Peters as saying.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
